00:02:41.770 --> 00:02:43.730
Now, I said this is just the
same thing as the Pythagorean

00:02:43.730 --> 00:02:44.229
theorem.

00:02:44.229 --> 00:02:45.040
Why?

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:51.780
Well, if we were to construct a
right triangle right over here,

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:53.320
